    </p>

    <div class="coming-soon-card">
      <h2>Something new is on its way</h2>
      <p>
        I'm building a new website to keep you updated on my work at Lancashire County Council,
        share news, and make it easy for you to get in touch. Check back soon.
      </p>
    </div>

